<p>Alphabetical list of all users, including cell phone and home phone numbers. 'Idle' is the time since the user visited any page or submitted any form.</p>

<hr>

<% for user in @users -%>
<p>
  <bold><%= user.last_name %>, <%= user.first_name %></bold>
  <%= if user.last_request_at != nil : "<br>Idle: #{time_ago_in_words(user.last_request_at)}" end %>
  <%= if user.cell_phone != '' : "<br>Cell: #{user.cell_phone}" end -%>
  <%= if user.home_phone != '' : "<br>Home: #{user.home_phone}" end -%>
</p>
<% end -%>